<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="anyway-adv">anyway <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'eniweɪ/    美 /'eniweɪ/  </p>
<p><a href="anyhow">句子副词</a></p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>无论如何；反正：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’m too tired to study anymore; anyway, I’m getting hungry.
我太累，学不下去了，反正我也饿了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>尽管如此：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He didn't enjoy washing his car, but it was so dirty that he did it anyway.
他不喜欢洗车，但是车太脏了，所以他还是洗了。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>至少：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Let's think about it for a while, for a few days anyway.
让我们想一想，至少考虑几天。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>对了；好吧；总之：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Anyway, let's forget about that for the moment.
好吧，咱们暂时不要提这件事了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Anyway, I have to go now.
对了，我现在得走了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Anyway, doing what you love is wonderful.
总之，做自己喜欢的事是令人愉快的。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>What a terrible experience! <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ , you’re safe now — that’s the main thing.  （2013 江西）<br />
A.Anyway<br />
B.Besides<br />
C.Otherwise<br />
D.Therefore  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. A  </p></div>